headline: Are Wall Street Analysts Predicting AvalonBay Communities Stock Will Climb or Sink?
summary: While AvalonBay Communities has considerably lagged behind the broader market over the past 52 weeks, Wall Street analysts maintain a moderately optimistic outlook about the stock’s prospects.
